@lucyperu recording vocals for a new song on her upcoming #musicfornight EP
Happy Mother’s Day to the absolute best. Love you Mom!!!!
New interview with @canvasrebel, discussing my new company @soundsugarmusic (and my undying love for Jon Brion). Link in bio.

My dad is the kindest, gentlest human you’ll ever meet, the best listener, the quickest with a surprise zinger, and just the most calming presence I could have grown up around. He’s a dispenser of great wisdom, classic dad puns, and a ridiculously fun PopPop to Noah. Happy Father’s Day!!!!!
My sister’s new inspiring summer anthem Unstuck is out today! (I co-produced, mixed and mastered.) Go sis!!
Had a nice chat with @boldjourneymag about imposter syndrome, its antidote, and “sharpening the axe.” Link in bio.

So thrilled that @lucyperu ‘s stirring new EP of cinematic dream pop is out today. Had an amazing time co-producing, mixing and mastering this with her. Each song is like a perfect little short film and the whole thing casts a peaceful spell. Please enjoy. With lovely performances by @brendanbuckley @earl_harvin and @nayanna
#hollywoodglamour

Tonight! Apogee presents “Saluting Peter Gabriel”, mixed by Bob Clearmountain, with Lyle Workman, Scrote, Colin Haye, Mike Viola, myself, Patrick Warren, Ryan Brown, Stan Cotey and tons more!! So thrilled to be playing with these beasts. Proceeds benefit UCLA Institute of the Environment & Sustainability. Tickets are sold out but there should be more available at the door. Doors open at 7.
